<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Upside</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study upside">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Upside</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Travel that takes&nbsp;<br />care of business</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Business Travel Application</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded yellow">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">The founder of Priceline.com set his sights on business travel, and&nbsp;we&nbsp;created a product that turns the industry on its head.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded gray">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Travel for business has never been worse
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Before you even get to the plane, a maze of shifting flights, hotels and meetings awaits you. And there's no real incentive for anyone to try harder.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Show users the formula, and reward them
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            A model that you can tinker with is paired with real savings and gift cards to empower and motivate users.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Brand System</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Front-end Development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded orange">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">What’s in it for you</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Upside rewards users who are flexible—with real gift cards to their favorite retailers—all while saving their company money. We created a series of intuitive infographics to explain this concept.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark sr-right">
            <img src="./images/work/upside/rewards.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/airplane-banner.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow yellow">
        <img src="./images/work/upside/details-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
        <img src="./images/work/upside/details-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-left">
        <img src="./images/work/upside/details-3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-right">
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column order-top-xs half-md gray">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Goodbye, forms</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Getting the details of your trip shouldn't feel like an interrogation. We rethought and resequenced how users plan their trips, so they understand what's going on and why.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block dark-purple">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/plane-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/plane.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-left">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Try a trip on for size</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We got rid of sluggish search results of endless, identical-looking options. Instead, users can easily change any part of their trips, and quickly see the impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row upside-interface">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-bottom">
            <img src="./images/work/upside/interface.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <img src="./images/work/upside/interface-bg1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-left sr-delay-double">
          <img src="./images/work/upside/interface-bg2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-right sr-delay-double">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/terminal-banner.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md gray">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Business travel visualized</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Layovers, cabin class, room accomodations&mdash;all of these are tangible experiences. Our system of visualizations let users actually see how their options play out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow purple">
        <img src="./images/work/upside/visualized-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
        <img src="./images/work/upside/visualized-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-bottom">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block dark-purple">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/section-6-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/section-6-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-right">
      <img src="./images/work/upside/section-6-3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-delay-double sr-reveal">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-left">
            <img src="./images/work/upside/find.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Stop waiting, start finding</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A staggered approach to travel&mdash;airfare and hotel in separate steps&mdash;keeps the user engaged while cleverly doing work in the background. The result: a magically 'instant' experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md purple">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Brave was the best and brightest in the room.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md gray">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">Brave does more than UX. They helped us think through the entire product — from design to user path to animation. When we needed a partner and some extra brainpower, Brave was the best and the brightest in the room.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Scott Case, <em>President, Upside</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/homezen" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
          <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/felix" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>
    <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
